<ListItem><Paragraph Foreground="{DynamicResource ColorBrush1}">如同大部分光源一样，它会融化一定范围内的<Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E9%9B%AA" Margin="0,0,0,-8">雪</local:MyTextButton></Underline>和<Underline><local:MyTextButton EventType="打开网页" EventData="https://zh.minecraft.wiki/w/%E5%86%B0" Margin="0,0,0,-8">冰</local:MyTextButton></Underline>。</Paragraph></ListItem>
